data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Auction Property. CONVENTIONAL, FHA AND VA FINANCING ACCEPTABLE, so not cash only! NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE! HVAC is 3y old, Water/Heater 2y old, and ROOF is 12 y old. House is insurable, and current policy amount for the year is $1600. Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this inviting haven beckons with its allure. A picturesque residence, boasting a charming facade, welcomes you to explore its exquisite interior. As you step inside, be greeted by the spaciousness of a newly remodeled abode. With three cozy bedrooms and two pristine bathrooms, this home is designed for comfort and functionality. The master suite, tucked away for privacy, features a modernized en-suite bath and a generous walk-in closet, offering both luxury and convenience. The heart of this abode is its newly renovated kitchen adorned with gleaming floors that exude elegance. Vaulted ceilings grace the living spaces, creating an airy ambiance that invites relaxation. The thoughtful layout, with its split bedroom plan, ensures ample privacy for all residents. A concrete driveway, flanked by gates on either side, adds a touch of security and convenience, providing ample space to park vehicles and store your cherished possessions. Whether it's your RV, boat, or other toys, this home accommodates your storage needs effortlessly. Entertainment and leisure await outdoors, where a screened-in pool glistens under the sun, inviting you to unwind and bask in its tranquility. The joy of a refreshing dip or hosting gatherings against this scenic backdrop becomes a regular indulgence. Practicality meets modern convenience with amenities such as public water and sewer, ensuring hassle-free living. Central air conditioning guarantees year-round comfort, while the meticulously maintained property promises ease of upkeep. This home embodies a harmonious blend of functionality, style, and comfort, offering an ideal canvas for creating cherished memories. Whether lounging by the pool or enjoying the comfort of the remodeled interiors, this sanctuary epitomizes the essence of gracious living.
